QuestData.Title: The Forward Push
QuestData.Description:
<Sharnax scratches her chin.>
The commander was right. The Primalists are calling reinforcements from the elemental planes.
<Sharnax smirks.>
It would be a shame if something happened to their gateways, $c.
QuestData.LogDescription: Obtain Misttouched, Earthen, and Iceforged gateway stones, and close the $7oa elemental gateways.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Speak with Sharnax at Gelikyr Overlook.
QuestData.RewardText: Looks like you made it in one piece.
